fields.name: 3-in-1
fields.subtitle: WINDSHIELD, WHEELS, AND DENT REPAIR PROTECTION
fields.description: Coverage for minor dent repair, windshield repair or replacement, and includes tire and wheel policy. Recommended for vehicles that spend a lot of time on the highway or parked on city streets.
fields.more_description:
This coverage includes

Minor Dent Repair

 
Easily removes minor dents and door dings
 
Developed by automobile manufacturers
 
Works from behind the vehicle's exterior
 
No sanding, painting or body fillers
 
Repairs are fast and friendly

Windshield repair

 
Save money - Windshield Repairs can cost as much as $1,000 or more
 
A professional technician will repair your damaged windshield
 
No sanding, painting or body fillers
 
Saves on costly windshield deductible

Tire and Wheel Coverage

 
Coverage includes 100% repair or replacement.
 
Reimbursement for a covered road hazard with no deductible or hidden fees for tires and mounting, wheels, balancing, valve stems, sales tax and customary labor charges.
 
Protects against blowouts, nails, glass, potholes and debris.
 
Toll-free sign and drive roadside service for tire related emergencies is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year.
*Limitations apply. See contract details for exact coverage.

fields.name: R.O.A.D key replacement
fields.subtitle: KEY PROTECTION
fields.description: Coverage for replacement of lost or stolen keys. This policy also includes emergency roadside assistance and car rental discounts. Recommended for vehicles with integrated key remotes.
fields.more_description:
This coverage includes

Key replacement service:

 
Key Replacement and Remote Replacement if a key is lost or stolen or destroyed
 
Lockout service covered up to $50 for services of a Plan Locksmith.

Emergency road service:

 
Tire Service - changing an inflated spare tire from mount to wheel
 
Battery Service - Attempting to start a vehicle with a booster battery
 
Delivery Service of emergency supplies - Delivery of an emergency supplies. Member pays for the cost of the materials that are delivered.
 
Custom Trip Rounting
 
Auto Rental Discounts from AVIS, Budget, Enterprise, Hertz and National.
 
Sales tax

fields.name: Excess Wear and Tear
fields.subtitle: VEHICLE  PROTECTION
fields.description: Coverage for cosmetic repairs to paint and upholstery, chipped or cracked glass,burned out bulbs, and more. Recommended for all leased vehicles.
fields.more_description:
This coverage includes

 
Tires
 
Scratched and chipped paint
 
Stains and spotting of upholstery and carpet
 
Chipped glass
 
Cracked head lamps
 
Burned out tail light
 
Windshield or mirror
 
Cuts, rips, crackes, burns, stains and spotting to the internal and cargo storage areas
 
Convertible tops, padded tops and vinyl tops
 
Molding, trim, bright metal and surrounding trim
 
Convertible tops, padded tops and vinyl tops
 
Bumpers, step bumpers and surrounding trim
 
Antennae
 
Name plate badge sand hood ornaments
 
Door, trunk and hatch handles
 
Scratches, chips, pits, rust, corrosion and cracks
 
Front and rear door, hatch and tailgate rubber deals
 
Lenses of head lamps, rear lamps and fog lights
 
Tail, turn signal and brake light lenses, sealed beams and halogen and light bulbs
 
Discoloration, stone bruises, sand damage and pits.

fields.name: Tire and Wheel Coverage
fields.subtitle: VEHICLE  PROTECTION
fields.description: Includes 24-hour nationwide roadside assistance and 100% repair or replacement of tires and wheels. Recommended for leased vehicles with wheels that are 17'' or larger.
fields.more_description:

From major causes of road hazards and yourself with roadside assistance including:

 
Debris
 
Potholes
 
Metal
 
Glass
 
Nails

100 percent repair or replacement reimbursement coverage for:

 
Tires and mounting
 
Valve stems
 
Wheels
 
Tire balancing
 
Customary labor charges
 
Sales tax

Bonus

Service for tie and wheel related emergencies 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year, anywhere nationwide

fields.h1: 3-in-1 windshield, wheels and dent repair vehicle protection
fields.meta_descripton:
A 3-in-1 policy combines coverage from windshield, wheels, and dent
repair policies.

fields.title: Car key replacement coverage for leased vehicles | Rodo Insurance
fields.meta_descripton: A key replacement can replace a lost, stolen, or damaged vehicle key.

fields.title: Excess wear and tear coverage for leased vehicles | Rodo Insurance
fields.meta_descripton:
An excess wear and tear policy will cover a variety of minor damage to
paint, glass, and upholstery

fields.title: Tire and wheel coverage for leased vehicles | Rodo Insurance
fields.meta_descripton: A tire and wheel policy will cover you in case of a flat tire or dented wheel.

fields.title: Enhanced coverage for leased vehicles | Rodo Insurance
fields.meta_descripton:
Rodo Insurance offers plans to cover unexpected expenses on leased cars
for up to 30 days after you take delivery.
